    }
  ]
}
7. Conclusion & Future Outlook
tokenizerArt successfully demonstrates that modern development tools like Foundry, combined with proven cryptographic standards and a modern web interface, can yield high-security, highly-accessible non-fungible assets. By respecting the strict rules of blockchain ownership, off-chain decentralized storage, and clear user experiences, tokenizerArt sets a clean benchmark for technical evaluations and future generative art implementations on EVM networks.